data.description: Located on the golf course associated with Grand Ridge Golf Club, in the much sought after subdivision of Willow Ridge, this spacious home offers sun room and breakfast area look out onto # 7 Tee! 4 bedrooms 3 full bathrooms, sun room, formal dining, laundry room, 2-car garage, granite counter tops and double oven. Bonus room off of very large primary bedroom. 1 year old roof, one new A/C unit, new flooring on 1st, tankless water heater, new garage door and brand new French front doors. Top rated schools!
